com.microsoft.azure.storage

Enum StorageErrorCode

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<StorageErrorCode>
      • com.microsoft.azure.storage.StorageErrorCode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<StorageErrorCode>

    public enum StorageErrorCode
extends Enum<StorageErrorCode>
    Represents error codes that may be returned by the Microsoft Azure storage services or the storage client library.
